      "user": {
        "title": "Set Up SecretSentry",
        "description": "SecretSentry scans your Home Assistant configuration for potential security issues like exposed secrets, insecure settings, and git hygiene problems.\n\n**Safety Note:** This integration performs ONLY local scanning. It does not connect to the internet, enumerate other instances, or use external services.\n\nClick Submit to set up SecretSentry with default settings. You can configure options after setup."
